title: West Brom's James McClean gets FA warning, but escapes ban - Keighleynews.co.uk
text:
West Brom's James McLean confronts Sunderland's Lee Cattermole after Albion's 1-0 win on Saturday. The Baggies midfielder has escaped a fine or suspension while both clubs have been reminded of their responsibilities following the melee which was sparked by McClean's actions.
 Keighleynews.co.uk.
